EYES ON. Create an eye-opening look in just a few simple steps using an eye cream, lash primer and mascara. 

Step 1. Apply three dots of LE LIFT Eye Cream under the eyes and tap in. Use your index finger to perform smoothing movements under the eye, and on the eyelid from the inner corner outward for a lifted and firmer appearance. 

Step 2. Coat the top lashes only with LA BASE MASCARA Volume and Care Lash Primer. 

Step 3. Apply LE VOLUME DE CHANEL Mascara in Noir to top and bottom lashes.

CHANEL BEAUTY LESSON – How to Play With Bold Colour
Makeup made modern with a vibrant twist. Achieve a bold, colourful look with #CometesCollective makeup artist @Valentina1121Li.

Step 1. Perfect your skin with LES BEIGES WATER-FRESH COMPLEXION TOUCH.
Step 2. Sweep OMBRE ESSENTIELLE in Lilas Poudré across the lid, tapping for intensity.
Step 3. Define the lash line with STYLO YEUX WATERPROOF in Cassis.
Step 4. Curl lashes and apply NOIR ALLURE mascara in Noir for eye-opening volume.
Step 5. Tap N°1 de CHANEL Lip and Cheek Balm in Lively Rosewood onto cheeks for a healthy glow.
Step 6. Finish with ROUGE COCO GLOSS in Rose Pulpe for a glossy touch.

@Noor.Mutsaers
